<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8"/>
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Sifr — Case Study</title>
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&family=Fraunces:wght@700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet"/>
  <style>
    *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
    :root{
      --forest:#1a3d2f;
      --forest-mid:#264f3a;
      --coral:#e8562a;
      --sand:#f5f0e8;
      --teal:#5bbfa0;
      --white:#fff;
      --muted:rgba(255,255,255,.55);
    }
    html{scroll-behavior:smooth}
    body{font-family:'Inter',sans-serif;background:var(--forest);color:var(--white);line-height:1.6}

    /* HERO */
    .hero{
      min-height:100vh;display:flex;flex-direction:column;
      align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      padding:80px 2rem 60px;text-align:center;
      position:relative;overflow:hidden;
    }
    .ring{
      position:absolute;border-radius:50%;pointer-events:none;
      border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.04);
      top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);
    }
    .ring:nth-child(1){width:600px;height:600px}
    .ring:nth-child(2){width:960px;height:960px}
    .tag{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:7px;
      background:rgba(91,191,160,.13);border:1px solid rgba(91,191,160,.28);
      color:var(--teal);font-size:.72rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.1em;
      text-transform:uppercase;padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:1.6rem;
    }
    .tag::before{content:'';width:6px;height:6px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--teal)}
    h1{
      font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
      font-size:clamp(3.2rem,9vw,7rem);
      line-height:.92;letter-spacing:-.025em;margin-bottom:1.4rem;
    }
    h1 .accent{color:var(--coral)}
    .hero-sub{
      font-size:1rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:460px;
      margin:0 auto 3rem;line-height:1.75;
    }
    .hero-sub strong{color:rgba(255,255,255,.85)}
    .phones{display:flex;align-items:flex-end;justify-content:center;gap:14px}
    .phones img{border-radius:24px;box-shadow:0 28px 70px rgba(0,0,0,.55);display:block}
    .phones .main img{width:195px}
    .phones .side img{width:150px;opacity:.7;transform:translateY(22px)}
    .scroll-cue{
      margin-top:56px;font-size:.7rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.25);
      letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;
      display:flex;flex-direction:column;align-items:center;gap:8px;
    }
    .scroll-cue::after{content:'';width:1px;height:38px;background:rgba(255,255,255,.12)}

    /* DIVIDER */
    hr{border:none;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.07);margin:0}

    /* FEATURE SCROLL */
    .feat-section{padding:80px 0}
    .feat-header{padding:0 2rem;max-width:1080px;margin:0 auto 2.5rem}
    .eyebrow{font-size:.7rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.14em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--teal);margin-bottom:.5rem}
    h2.title{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(1.9rem,4vw,3rem);line-height:1.1;color:var(--white)}
    .feat-scroll{
      display:flex;gap:1.4rem;padding:0 2rem;
      overflow-x:auto;scrollbar-width:none;-ms-overflow-style:none;
    }
    .feat-scroll::-webkit-scrollbar{display:none}
    .feat-card{
      flex:0 0 280px;
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.04);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.08);
      border-radius:18px;padding:22px;
    }
    .feat-card img{width:100%;border-radius:10px;margin-bottom:1rem;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.4)}
    .feat-chip{
      display:inline-block;font-size:.68rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.08em;
      text-transform:uppercase;padding:3px 9px;border-radius:20px;margin-bottom:.7rem;
    }
    .chip-teal{background:rgba(91,191,160,.18);color:var(--teal)}
    .chip-coral{background:rgba(232,86,42,.18);color:#f0855a}
    .chip-white{background:rgba(255,255,255,.09);color:rgba(255,255,255,.65)}
    .feat-card h3{font-size:.98rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:.35rem;color:var(--white)}
    .feat-card p{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.6}

    /* SHOWCASE */
    .showcase{background:rgba(255,255,255,.02);padding:80px 2rem}
    .block{
      max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto 72px;
      display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:5rem;align-items:center;
    }
    .block.flip{direction:rtl}
    .block.flip>*{direction:ltr}
    .block-text h3{
      font-family:'Fraunces',serif;
      font-size:clamp(1.6rem,3vw,2.3rem);line-height:1.1;
      color:var(--white);margin-bottom:.75rem;
    }
    .block-text p{font-size:.93rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75}
    .block-img{display:flex;justify-content:center}
    .block-img img{width:230px;border-radius:26px;box-shadow:0 28px 72px rgba(0,0,0,.5)}

    /* COLLAB */
    .collab{background:var(--forest-mid);padding:80px 2rem;text-align:center}
    .collab-inner{max-width:560px;margin:0 auto}
    .collab-inner h2{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:clamp(1.8rem,4vw,2.7rem);margin-bottom:1rem}
    .collab-inner p{font-size:.97rem;color:var(--muted);line-height:1.75;margin-bottom:2rem}
    .collab-card{
      background:rgba(255,255,255,.06);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.1);
      border-radius:14px;padding:20px 24px;
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;text-align:left;
    }
    .collab-icon{
      width:48px;height:48px;background:var(--coral);border-radius:11px;
      display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
      font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-size:1.4rem;flex-shrink:0;
    }
    .collab-card strong{display:block;font-size:.95rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--white)}
    .collab-card span{font-size:.82rem;color:var(--muted)}
    .play-link{
      display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;
      background:var(--coral);color:white;
      padding:12px 24px;border-radius:10px;
      font-size:.88rem;font-weight:600;text-decoration:none;
      margin-top:2rem;transition:opacity .15s;
    }
    .play-link:hover{opacity:.85}

    footer{
      padding:36px 2rem;text-align:center;
      font-size:.78rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,.2);
      border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,.06);
    }

    @media(max-width:720px){
      .block{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:2rem}
      .block.flip{direction:ltr}
      .phones .side{display:none}
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
  <div class="ring"></div>
  <div class="ring"></div>
  <div class="tag">Case Study &middot; Mobile App</div>
  <h1>Sifr<br><span class="accent">Halal banking</span></h1>
  <p class="hero-sub">The first <strong>Islamic banking app</strong> in the Netherlands &mdash; built in collaboration with INSIFR. Interest-free payments, goal-based saving, and principled investing.</p>
  <div class="phones">
    <div class="side"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Savings screen"/></div>
    <div class="main"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Overview screen"/></div>
    <div class="side"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Invest screen"/></div>
  </div>
  <div class="scroll-cue">Scroll</div>
</section>

<hr/>

<!-- FEATURE SCROLL -->
<div class="feat-section">
  <div class="feat-header">
    <div class="eyebrow">What the app does</div>
    <h2 class="title">Six screens, one vision</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="feat-scroll">
    <div class="feat-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Overview"/>
      <span class="feat-chip chip-teal">Overview</span>
      <h3>Everything at a glance</h3>
      <p>Total balance split across payment and savings accounts, with transactions and quick actions on the home screen.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Send money"/>
      <span class="feat-chip chip-coral">Payments</span>
      <h3>Send money in seconds</h3>
      <p>Full breakdown per transfer: amount, recipient, date, purpose, and balance after booking.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Save"/>
      <span class="feat-chip chip-teal">Savings</span>
      <h3>Save with a goal</h3>
      <p>Create savings jars for Zakaat, Hajj, holidays or a car &mdash; each with a visual progress bar.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Card"/>
      <span class="feat-chip chip-white">Card</span>
      <h3>Your Mastercard, always ready</h3>
      <p>Virtual debit card visible at any time. Add it to Google Wallet with one tap.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Donate"/>
      <span class="feat-chip chip-coral">Donate</span>
      <h3>Give when you can</h3>
      <p>Donate directly to Islamic charities and foundations right from the app.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feat-card">
      <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Invest"/>
      <span class="feat-chip chip-teal">Invest</span>
      <h3>Halal-screened stocks</h3>
      <p>Every stock gets a Halal score so you only invest in what aligns with your values.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<hr/>

<!-- SHOWCASE -->
<div class="showcase">

  <div class="block">
    <div class="block-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">Overview</div>
      <h3>A clear picture of your finances</h3>
      <p>The home screen shows the total balance split between payment and savings accounts. Transactions are categorised, searchable, and exportable. Paying takes a single tap.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="block-img"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Clear overview"/></div>
  </div>

  <div class="block flip">
    <div class="block-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">Savings</div>
      <h3>Goal-driven saving</h3>
      <p>Users create separate savings jars for concrete goals &mdash; including Islamic obligations like Zakaat and Hajj. Each jar shows exactly how much is still needed.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="block-img"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Savings goals"/></div>
  </div>

  <div class="block">
    <div class="block-text">
      <div class="eyebrow">Investing</div>
      <h3>Invest with principles</h3>
      <p>The investment module scores every stock for halal compliance. Buy and sell directly in the app, knowing your portfolio stays aligned with Islamic financial values.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="block-img"><img src="data:image/png;base64," alt="Investing"/></div>
  </div>

</div>

<hr/>

<!-- COLLAB -->
<div class="collab">
  <div class="collab-inner">
    <div class="eyebrow" style="color:var(--teal)">Collaboration</div>
    <h2>Built together with INSIFR</h2>
    <p>This app was developed in close collaboration with the owners of Sifr &mdash; from UX strategy and interface design to embedding Islamic financial principles into every screen.</p>
    <div class="collab-card">
      <div class="collab-icon">S</div>
      <div>
        <strong>INSIFR &times; Your Name</strong>
        <span>Design &amp; development collaboration &mdash; 2025</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <br/>
    <a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.insifr.sifr" target="_blank" class="play-link">
      View on Google Play &rarr;
    </a>
  </div>
</div>

<footer>&copy; 2025 &mdash; Sifr case study &mdash; In collaboration with INSIFR</footer>

</body>
</html>
